.Dd June 29, 2026
.Dt XF-VM 7
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm xf-vm
.Nd XF virtual machine and execution model
.Sh DESCRIPTION
XF compiles parsed source into a VM-oriented intermediate form and then executes it in a runtime that supports scalar values, collections, formatting, records, and core built-ins.
.Sh RUNTIME FEATURES
.Bl -bullet
.It
stack-based or opcode-driven execution
.It
special record-processing variables
.It
core built-in namespaces
.It
garbage-collection support
.It
optional multithreaded helpers
.It
SIMD support in selected code paths
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr xf-lang 7 ,
.Xr xf-gc 7 ,
.Xr xf-mt 7
